name: massage
description:
"massage" is the 9th song off my new beattape "souls" releaseing August 27, 2021. its a brain massage. 

the cover art was generated by AI using the text prompt "soul massage." maybe the AI was on some sort of self medicating virus to create this mind bending piece. 

Bop your head and enjoy the music. If you purchase this piece, hit me up on twitter @ryanartwalker and I will send you the album with high quality AIFF files!
